    ::> delete character under cursor from
    ::> reverse-i-search or buffer, sending a [%clr ~]
    ::> if the buffer is empty.
    ::
    ^+  .
    ?^  ris
      ?:  =(~ str.u.ris)
        ta-bel
      .(str.u.ris (scag (dec (lent str.u.ris)) str.u.ris))
    ?:  =(0 pos.inp)
      ?~  buf.say.inp
