    ::> when a history entry is accepted, clear search
    ::> and edit overlay, save current buffer to {old.hit}
    ::
    ^+  .
    =.  ris  ~
    =.  lay.hit  ~
    ?:  ?|  ?=($~ buf.say.inp)
